			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; " >
												<DIV>Bards are not tanks.&nbsp; We may wear plate, but we are not tanks.&nbsp; We are a support class.&nbsp; Support class does not equal tank.&nbsp; Tanks need taunt.&nbsp; Support classes don't.&nbsp; Get over the "plate = tank" mentality since it is not true.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>While I don't see the need for bards to get taunt.&nbsp; Adding it wouldn't be hard.&nbsp; Instead of giving us a +5 str +5 atk version of Zek in the next expansion just make a song opposite of our agro reducer song.&nbsp; Two birds, one stone.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>What I do have an issue with is why something that shouldn't be an issue at all is in our top ten list.&nbsp; There are many things that would be nice is certain situations.&nbsp; These would be neat toys but really don't serve the community as a whole.&nbsp; Let the devs focus on things that are true issues (fizzles, song fades bug, etc) rather than very situational toys.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
																																		<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 100; overflow: hidden;">
														<p>Jarroll Lonelysong - The Commune
Bard of Xegony

/join xegony.bards:bards
							</div>
																
