						<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#0C142B" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; " >
												<BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
-Taha- wrote:<BR>Bards do not need taunt, it is sad to see it in top 10 issues. We need other stuff fixed, bard is a support class not tank.<BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV></DIV>
<P>A lot of bards disagree.&nbsp; And by taunt it isn't being asked that SOE give bards a taunt hotkey.&nbsp; Nor is it being asked to greatly increase the taunt generated by all of our songs.&nbsp; What is being asked for is that we have a song or aa or skill that will allow us to generate more agro faster than the time it takes for us to do so with our chants in order that we can tank mobs that are being tanked by classes that are less of a tank than we are.&nbsp; Sure, I can use chants to pull agro.&nbsp; But, by the time I have generated enough agro to do so, the mob has already killed three caster class players.</P>
<P>I see a very good need for it.&nbsp; If you don't, then don't use it.&nbsp; Some of us constantly see situations where it is a needed ability in order to help out our group or raid.&nbsp; Just because you don't see a use for it doesn't mean it doesn't have one.&nbsp; The fact that it is high on the new top ten additions show that others don't agree with your assessment either.&nbsp; This is akin to saying bards don't need to wear plate either.&nbsp; Granted, most of the time I don't get hit, so don't really get a lot of benefit from the plate.&nbsp; Other times I do, so I am glad I have it.&nbsp; It is about situations.&nbsp; </P>
<P>Personally, I would rather not tank in any fashion.&nbsp; It detracts from my contribution to the group or raid.&nbsp; However, I want it to be my choice.&nbsp; If I see a situation that deems I tank, then I want the means in which to accomplish it, better dps, better mitigation, and better taunting so that I can do so instead of being forced to just sit back and watch other classes do so just because they have better agro gaining ability than I do.</P>
<P>Polara</P>
																		
