<DIV>Well, being 65th level and watching all the times othesr have died because there was no effective way to gain agro in order to save them I have to disagree with this completely.&nbsp; Add in the fact that gaining agro with chants at the high end game isn't an effective method to gain agro as it takes way too long to build up the required agro in order to get over agro generated from any form of healing, snaring, dotting, or nuking prior to the current reduction in said agro generated (see other posts regarding this).&nbsp; Being 65th I haven't found any effective means to gain agro over other classes previously stated, effectively shutting me down as a suragate tank.&nbsp; Any proported tools we have are based entirely on the same addage of the bard class, we can kill any mob that doesn't have extremely high hp regen, doesn't summon, and isn't a caster, the only thing it requires is an excessive amount of time.&nbsp; And time is the killer in this whole debate.&nbsp; Being able to gain agro off a mob is easy, once the rest of the party is dead.&nbsp; But by then it is a totally mute point.&nbsp; Add the continued support for being able to gain agro in some fashion also states that it isn't the low end bards that is being hit with this, but rather it is over the entire life of a bard.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Polara</DIV>
																		
