			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; " >
												I would just like to add that at the low - mid end it is ridiculously easy to get agro from a mob once you have mes, it gets even easier once you have charm at lvl 27 as this generates huge amounts of agro for the level we're at compared to the amount of agro other spells generate (chanter death anyone).<br><br>At high levels this becomes less viable because our measly charm and mes spells stop working and as they are also such low level they cause somewhat less agro than the wizard that just crited for 7K damage.<br><br>This is why I think that the agro problem is more pronounced at high levels than at low levels and as such that's where it should be fixed.
																																		<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 100; overflow: hidden;">
